text: Leirinmore () is a crofting township in the parish of Durness on the northern coastline of Scotland, in Sutherland, Scottish Highlands. It is in the Scottish council area of Highland. Smoo Cave is located close to Leirinmore. ==References== ==See also== *Smoo Cave Category:Populated places in Sutherland Leirinmore
